      "docs": "Role enum for TypeEntry (struct / enum / type alias). Declares the DDD / Clean Architecture role of a data type. Breaking change from prior track: CompositionRoot (unit) and PrimaryAdapter (unit) variants added (17 variants total). CompositionRoot is restricted to cli_composition layer only (KindLayerConstraint). PrimaryAdapter is restricted to cli_driver layer only (KindLayerConstraint + NoRoleInMethodSignature). All 15 pre-existing variants are unchanged in shape; the 6 public constructor/accessor methods are unchanged in signature and constructor semantics. Only variant_name / string conversion logic and exhaustive consumers must gain arms for the 2 new unit variants.",
