      "docs": "Payload-free discriminant enum spanning all DataRole (17 variants after this track), ContractRole (4 variants), and FunctionRole (2 variants) variants — 23 total. Breaking change: CompositionRoot and PrimaryAdapter discriminants added (both unit variants), and FunctionRole discriminants FreeFunction / UseCaseFunction are included so role-targeted lint rules can apply to FunctionEntry items. from_data_role, from_contract_role, from_function_role, and variant_name match arms must cover all variants. The pub(crate) ALL, DATA_ROLES, CONTRACT_ROLES, and FUNCTION_ROLES array constants are not part of the public API surface and require no catalogue entry.",
